sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant PV as PromptDetailView
    participant DB as Debounce Task
    participant MC as ModelContext
    participant SD as SwiftData Store

    U->>PV: Edit title/content
    PV->>DB: Schedule debounced save
    DB->>PV: Update updatedAt
    PV->>MC: Save context
    MC->>SD: Persist changes
